<template>
  <gmap-map
    ref="mapRef"
    :zoom="7"
    :center="center"
    map-type-id="roadmap"
    style="width: 100%; height: 500px;"
  >
    <gmap-marker
      v-for="(m, index) in markers"
      :key="index"
      :position="m.location"
      :clickable="true"
      :draggable="true"
      @click="center=m.location"
    />
    <gmap-heatmap-layer
      :data="markers"
      :options="{maxIntensity: 120, dissipating: false}"
    />
  </gmap-map>
</template>
<script>
  import { gmapApi } from 'gmap-vue';

  export default {
    computed: {
      google: gmapApi,
      markers() {
        if (this.google) {
          return [
            { location: new google.maps.LatLng({ lat: 3, lng: 101 }), weight: 100 },
            { location: new google.maps.LatLng({ lat: 5, lng: 99 }), weight: 50  },
            { location: new google.maps.LatLng({ lat: 6, lng: 97 }), weight: 80 }
          ];
        }
        return [];
      },
    },
  };
</script>
